data.description: This nice ranch features a great family room with F/P, kitchen with big dining area, pantry, big laundry room, 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, an additional room for an office or play room,  an attached big carport, all sitting on a large fenced lot with plenty of rooms for all kinds of outside activities and entertainment. There are two storage buildings in the back yard and also a round concrete driveway on the front. Great location, with easy access to Hwy 84. Only few minutes to Elba or Enterprise.  Well established area.  House will need some repairs and updates. This is a VA foreclosure to be sold as is, no repairs. Home built prior to 1978, lead paint potentially exist. Alabama Right of Redemption may affect this asset. This property may qualify for seller financing (Vendee). Seller does not guarantee or warrant title to the property.
